Tamasheq: Addălen wǝn tăǧrest ăntani yettiwăzdayen deɣ akalen wi n Afella, imăzzaɣen wi n Italy emhăren deɣ timcecwărin n amăḍal d timădashen tin Olimpik. 
English: Tamasheq: He has been in Italy for the last two weeks, and has been training with the team.

text: Maroochydore ǝnta ezzaran , sadisat tǝtbaqqa n Noosa wan ǝssǝn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Maroochydore ǝnta ezzaran, sadisat tǝtbaqqa n Noosa wan ǝssǝn. 
English: Maroochydore and Noosa are both in the Northern Territory.

text: Michael Schumacher assimda aššal net andarran darat Alonso fal aɣăšod n toruft net daɣ tǝmăɣinnănen ajotnen alwaq wan aššal.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Michael Schumacher assimda aššal net andarran darat Alonso fal aɣăšod n toruft net daɣ tǝmăɣinnănen ajotnen alwaq wan aššal. 
English: Michael Schumacher has been named as the best driver of the year by the German magazine Auto Bild.

text: Tetati ɣas war teddub ad tekken taɣara yehussayen deɣ tamudri n ibaraḍen wi yekkanin addal miɣ ahal.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tetati ɣas war teddub ad tekken taɣara yehussayen deɣ tamudri n ibaraḍen wi yekkanin addal miɣ ahal. 
English: The first step is to find a place to live.

text: ǝndar has ătkul n ǝsifran w-ǝnfănen tăzzort n et fal as ǝmnăɣan daɣ Addal tan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: ǝndar has ătkul n ǝsifran w-ǝnfănen tăzzort n et fal as ǝmnăɣan daɣ Addal tan. 
English: Tamasheq: The first of the three books of the Qur'an is the most important.

text: Agamay usnan isken-d, tuntawin rnint ugarent dag PS miden.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Agamay usnan isken-d, tuntawin rnint ugarent dag PS miden. 
English: The PS has been accused of being a party to the corruption of the election.

text: Yeddubi ad illi daɣ amas-nit kal assuf miɣ haret iyen cund methanol, haret waɣ ak-isdarɣal miɣ ak-yenɣ.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Yeddubi ad illi daɣ amas-nit kal assuf miɣ haret iyen cund methanol, haret waɣ ak-isdarɣal miɣ ak-yenɣ. 
English: Tamasheq: The main component of the alcohol is methanol, which is a chemical compound that is found in the form of water.

text: Ɣas idracen wi n lkarita, wergi tikerẓi miɣ aramaɣ ta full ad tekked timsirin n PA ak asacilan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ɣas idracen wi n lkarita, wergi tikerẓi miɣ aramaɣ ta full ad tekked timsirin n PA ak asacilan. 
English: The government has said it will not allow the sale of any new PA aircraft to any country that does not have a legal basis for such a sale.

text: Akǎrǎš n torfen ajotnen ewǎy id har ajudi aksǝdǎn tan ajotnen fal abǎra tan , hǎrat id ewǎyǎn s uɣna n tǎqtiya tan daɣ assexǎt ǝ amukǝn n tǝɣǝswen ǝmmǎr uɣšǎd .
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Akǎrǎš n torfen ajotnen ewǎy id har ajudi aksǝdǎn tan ajotnen fal abǎra tan, hǎrat id ewǎyǎn s uɣna n tǎqtiya tan daɣ assexǎt ǝ amukǝn n tǝɣǝswen ǝmmǎr uɣšǎd. 
English: The first thing to do is to get a good night's sleep.

text: Kel farak wǝn ǝnušaman allăɣen as awen ăddobat ad awi almud daɣ armud n torhinna tan kanser, torhǝnna tan tǝbăqqaten, SIDA d tănănnăɣat daɣ addawla tan war- ha assăhăt, s ǝddikod n tămudre tan ǝmirhanăn wǝn torhǝnna tan kanser tan ǝfafan ogdăh ǝd tazune n addawla tan t-ǝlănen tabăɣort hullan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Kel farak wǝn ǝnušaman allăɣen as awen ăddobat ad awi almud daɣ armud n torhinna tan kanser, torhǝnna tan tǝbăqqaten, SIDA d tănănnăɣat daɣ addawla tan war- ha assăhăt, s ǝddikod n tămudre tan ǝmirhanăn wǝn torhǝnna tan kanser tan ǝfafan ogdăh ǝd tazune n addawla tan t-ǝlănen tabăɣort hullan. 
English: The disease is caused by a virus that is transmitted by mosquitoes.

text: Ehud Ur, emăsăɣar n teɣăre tan assexăt daɣ Inǝversǝte tan Dalhousie daɣ Halifax, Nova Scotia tolas amănokăl n ăšrut wan assexăt d sians n taggăyt tan torhǝnna tan jăbet n addăwla wan Kanada exyăz as utăr eha har ajjudi ǝšǝlăn net win tǝzărăt..
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ehud Ur, emăsăɣar n teɣăre tan assexăt daɣ Inǝversǝte tan Dalhousie daɣ Halifax, Nova Scotia tolas amănokăl n ăšrut wan assexăt d sians n taggăyt tan torhǝnna tan jăbet n addăwla wan Kanada exyăz as utăr eha har ajjudi ǝšǝlăn net win tǝzărăt.. 
English: Tamasheq: Ehud Ur, emăsăɣar n teɣăre tan assexăt daɣ Inǝversǝte tan Dalhousie daɣ Halifax, Nova Scotia tolas amănokăl n ăšrut wan assexăt d sians n taggăyt tan torhǝnna tan jăbet n addăwla wan Canada exyăz as utăr eha har ajjudi �

text: Win deɣ ărrawen zăhatălen brin tigăwt n alas, idit” tăggen ǝmuggăn iha gafa , d akennăs, d tebeddi deɣ udem n tanăṭ ful irit n ăssemmessu n tiyyitiwin-nsen , idit wer addubin ăsemmessu-nit s ibarăqqăten win bennan .
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Win deɣ ărrawen zăhatălen brin tigăwt n alas, idit” tăggen ǝmuggăn iha gafa, d akennăs, d tebeddi deɣ udem n tanăṭ ful irit n ăssemmessu n tiyyitiwin-nsen, idit wer addubin ăsemmessu-nit s ibarăqqăten win bennan. 
English: Tamasheq: I am not a prophet, but I am a prophet of the Lord.

text: Addint addoben a tan assirhan ăsusij n aman ammidăsnen ǝjašnen adu s tamadalt d tǝnăšărmăyen.

Tamasheq: Addint addoben a tan assirhan ăsusij n aman ammidăsnen ǝjašnen adu s tamadalt d tǝnăšărmăyen. 
English: The first step in the process is to find a suitable place to live.

text: Haret n addunet aɣilen tǝrmit n ttihurga tǝ yemunnin hullan atiwăknanet yedduet ad suḍuhnet hullan.

English: Tamasheq: Haret n addunet aɣilen tǝrmit n ttihurga tǝ yemunnin hullan atiwăknanet yedduet ad suḍuhnet hullan.

text: Potro ijraw asăfar n azer net mušam addobat uɣil n azzoj har ajudi.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Potro ijraw asăfar n azer net mušam addobat uɣil n azzoj har ajudi. 
English: Potro was beaten by Novak Djokovic in the second round of the ATP Finals.

text: Sit ful awǝn wer nteg a yeclayen : tadarsi n tădawla, iban kaffuḍ d tămettant deɣ tihrăyet.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Sit ful awǝn wer nteg a yeclayen : tadarsi n tădawla, iban kaffuḍ d tămettant deɣ tihrăyet. 
English: Tamasheq: Sit ful awǝn wer nteg a yeclayen : tadarsi n tădawla, iban kaffuḍ d tămettant deɣ tihrăyet.

text: Alxăkum n aɣrem wan Amsterdam d Anne Frank Museum allăɣen as ahišk assirhan-t biffen tolas eqqal xatar ǝ- ăssexăt n aljămaɣăt fal as ǝšwar aftaqat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alxăkum n aɣrem wan Amsterdam d Anne Frank Museum allăɣen as ahišk assirhan-t biffen tolas eqqal xatar ǝ- ăssexăt n aljămaɣăt fal as ǝšwar aftaqat. 
English: The Amsterdam Anne Frank Museum is a museum dedicated to the life and work of the Dutch explorer and explorer of the Americas, Anne Frank.

text: Lăɣtor ilkăm ǝ-aššăreɣa wan ăwikkăl n ămaskăl n torhinna s wen ehe tuzănt n ămirhăn d addinat wǝ yădnen fal ad war t-ămiskăl torhinna daɣ addinat wi yădnen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Lăɣtor ilkăm ǝ-aššăreɣa wan ăwikkăl n ămaskăl n torhinna s wen ehe tuzănt n ămirhăn d addinat wǝ yădnen fal ad war t-ămiskăl torhinna daɣ addinat wi yădnen. 
English: The first step is to find a good place to live.

text: Tăggăyt tan Demokrati d Aššăreɣa daɣ Haïti tǝjă ehătel fărak tan ǝjănen ăllăɣăt nen as tăqqǝmt n ălɣaskăr n ălxer wan ăddăwla tan Nepal ewăyăn id turhăna s war hǝn otesăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tăggăyt tan Demokrati d Aššăreɣa daɣ Haïti tǝjă ehătel fărak tan ǝjănen ăllăɣăt nen as tăqqǝmt n ălɣaskăr n ălxer wan ăddăwla tan Nepal ewăyăn id turhăna s war hǝn otesăn. 
English: Tamasheq: The Democratic Republic of Haiti has been in a state of emergency for the past two months.

text: Turna i yettaltaɣen miɣ axuten n tiniri i yeddubin ad enɣen ddunet waǧi antani afat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Turna i yettaltaɣen miɣ axuten n tiniri i yeddubin ad enɣen ddunet waǧi antani afat. 
English: Tamasheq: I am not a fan of the idea of a new religion.

text: Arrăwen wǝ yrinin s ămcewcaw n ahalal miɣ iban ăzeggez deɣ haraten hun tahuri tan ăɣărbaz, bucan ăddubin ăzeggez deɣ haraten aran iman-nesen ămuken-nesen hund ăddalen n tăkrikara miɣ akayad n ărrusum wi ran miɣ ăfanaɣ n tiwinas wala utunen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Arrăwen wǝ yrinin s ămcewcaw n ahalal miɣ iban ăzeggez deɣ haraten hun tahuri tan ăɣărbaz, bucan ăddubin ăzeggez deɣ haraten aran iman-nesen ămuken-nesen hund ăddalen n tăkrikara miɣ akayad n ărrusum wi ran miɣ ăfanaɣ n tiwinas wala utunen. 
English: The first thing to do is to find out if the area is suitable for camping.

text: Daɣ awatay ǝyyan, awadim tǝjraw torhinna addobat a tat asammaskal daɣ 10 har 15 n awadim.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ awatay ǝyyan, awadim tǝjraw torhinna addobat a tat asammaskal daɣ 10 har 15 n awadim. 
English: The number of people who have been infected with the virus has risen to more than 1,000.

text: Alwaq wa id azzukat akinnas darat as ămmewayăn addinat wǝ ahyajnen s lăɣtor, ǝddikod n 40 n addinat iyyad attǝrmasnen aqqiman id daɣ aɣalay tolas unjăyan s ujiš n takărmut.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa id azzukat akinnas darat as ămmewayăn addinat wǝ ahyajnen s lăɣtor, ǝddikod n 40 n addinat iyyad attǝrmasnen aqqiman id daɣ aɣalay tolas unjăyan s ujiš n takărmut. 
English: The first known settlement in the area was made by the Romans in the 1st century BC.

text: Amnukăl Ugustus ǝnta a-ǎzzǎran attǎkal n-laqtortan daɣ ǝššǎɣal tolas, amossan ɣarid taqqǝmt n-laqtortan tan Rome tazzǎrat maret taxdim ḍarat kǝnnasen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amnukăl Ugustus ǝnta a-ǎzzǎran attǎkal n-laqtortan daɣ ǝššǎɣal tolas, amossan ɣarid taqqǝmt n-laqtortan tan Rome tazzǎrat maret taxdim ḍarat kǝnnasen. 
English: The Roman emperor Augustus was the first to use the term Roman Republic.

text: šafer ǝja ahăyoj maqqoran daɣ eɣăf net.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: šafer ǝja ahăyoj maqqoran daɣ eɣăf net. 
English: Tamasheq: The first of the three books of the Qur'an.

text: “ ǝssewăd as n-ǝla ămarăd mustăn 4 s ǝba-s tan t-ǝjrăw torhǝnna tan jăbet”.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: “ ǝssewăd as n-ǝla ămarăd mustăn 4 s ǝba-s tan t-ǝjrăw torhǝnna tan jăbet”. 
English: Tamasheq: “We have to be careful with the 4 s.”

text: War tdubbid ad tezdayed turna tan ssem, bacin as tecwaḍeḍ awadem yessuɣel d awa ila deɣ tarfa nit, ezday inin awadem waɣ iswa miɣ ikca ssem.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War tdubbid ad tezdayed turna tan ssem, bacin as tecwaḍeḍ awadem yessuɣel d awa ila deɣ tarfa nit, ezday inin awadem waɣ iswa miɣ ikca ssem. 
English: Tamasheq: War is a war of the people, not of the rulers.

text: Awen orawid s-ǝmudǎlan sikun taba t-alabǎsat fal bǝtmǝna wan addal tolas teyatir ǝman net t-omar addinat s tesăse net taba.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Awen orawid s-ǝmudǎlan sikun taba t-alabǎsat fal bǝtmǝna wan addal tolas teyatir ǝman net t-omar addinat s tesăse net taba. 
English: Tamasheq: The first thing that I want to do is to make sure that the people of the world know that the Quran is the only true religion.

text: Aerosmith iftay konser tan net wǝ- aqqimnen daɣ ăsikil nasan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Aerosmith iftay konser tan net wǝ- aqqimnen daɣ ăsikil nasan. 
English: Aerosmith will play a show at the Arena in Las Vegas on Saturday.

text: Kud trid ideg yuhaẓ ideg wa llan icilan, agel hik.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Kud trid ideg yuhaẓ ideg wa llan icilan, agel hik. 
English: Tamasheq: I am not a prophet, but a teacher.

text: Tella talɣiwin aǧatent n aflam full iwetyan.35 mm ta tecwaḍen hullan ta n (36 full 24 mm).

Tamasheq: Tella talɣiwin aǧatent n aflam full iwetyan.35 mm ta tecwaḍen hullan ta n (36 full 24 mm). 
English: The film is shot in 35 mm format.

text: Daɣ elwaq wad awaẓlu waɣ itiwazzay, Disney tegdalti: ful innin tickets war timaskalen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ elwaq wad awaẓlu waɣ itiwazzay, Disney tegdalti: ful innin tickets war timaskalen. 
English: Disney has said that the company will not be able to sell tickets for the event.

text: Epizod fuk n ăddăl ǝjă fal muduɣ n ălkǝttăb itiwassănǝn dǝhen ǝttǝr ăfăhăm n muduɣ wen s tǝnfusen ăjotnen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Epizod fuk n ăddăl ǝjă fal muduɣ n ălkǝttăb itiwassănǝn dǝhen ǝttǝr ăfăhăm n muduɣ wen s tǝnfusen ăjotnen. 
English: The Epizod is a series of events that began in the first century BC and continued until the end of the third century BC.

text: Ekran tan n talavizyon ajotnen ansan daɣ ǝdagan ajotnen daɣ Roma ǝ- ad ǝkyidan addinat daɣ axtifat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ekran tan n talavizyon ajotnen ansan daɣ ǝdagan ajotnen daɣ Roma ǝ- ad ǝkyidan addinat daɣ axtifat. 
English: The Roman Empire was the most powerful empire in the world.

text: Sophocles d Aristophanes antenni musen addinet wi kanen almăsrax, miden ulaɣen, ǝknan ăweẓlu ǝyen ǝhussay daɣ tăsekla n ǝkkălen imdan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Sophocles d Aristophanes antenni musen addinet wi kanen almăsrax, miden ulaɣen, ǝknan ăweẓlu ǝyen ǝhussay daɣ tăsekla n ǝkkălen imdan. 
English: Sophocles: Aristophanes was a poet, philosopher, and dramatist.

text: ăddăl fuk ehăk năsǝxătăn ǝ-ălkǝttăbăn wǝ-s he ǝttǝrăn ărătan alwăq wa ǝd osăn ehăn wan ălkǝttăbăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: ăddăl fuk ehăk năsǝxătăn ǝ-ălkǝttăbăn wǝ-s he ǝttǝrăn ărătan alwăq wa ǝd osăn ehăn wan ălkǝttăbăn. 
English: The first thing to do is to find out if the person is a criminal.

text: Daɣ asuɣen kud trid ad tessitid tăɣuyit, daɣ wa n anfu kud trid ad tessitid tăzla-nit.

text: Teddubid ad tenhayed piramyds daɣ tihay, teddubid daɣ aten tenhayed daɣ asusem dat ad isentu asihar.

Tamasheq: Teddubid ad tenhayed piramyds daɣ tihay, teddubid daɣ aten tenhayed daɣ asusem dat ad isentu asihar. 
English: Tamasheq: The pyramids are built on the top of the mountains, the pyramids are built on the top of the valleys.

text: Llan iweẓlan wi kanen diɣ cund agadel n awuten n tiniri miɣ wi n aman, asiwer, acaweḍ n igḍaḍ, atireggac dag igelmam, akayad n isalen full tameddurt n imudiren.

English: The island is a popular tourist destination, with a wide variety of activities, from fishing to hiking, to cycling and kayaking.

text: Ellsworth Land ymus akal Wa yhan ajous n Peninsula, inharajas ijiriw Wan Billingshausen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ellsworth Land ymus akal Wa yhan ajous n Peninsula, inharajas ijiriw Wan Billingshausen. 
English: Ellsworth Land and the Peninsula, in the western part of the island, are located in the administrative territorial entity of the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador.

text: South Paul Traverse( migh abaraqqa Wa yermadhen) yougeg fel McMurdo Station aylan1600km dagh ijjiriw Wan Russ.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: South Paul Traverse( migh abaraqqa Wa yermadhen) yougeg fel McMurdo Station aylan1600km dagh ijjiriw Wan Russ. 
English: South Paul Traverse( migh abaraqqa Wa yermadhen) yougeg fel McMurdo Station aylan1600km dagh ijjiriw Wan Russ.

text: Iceǧrin hulan fel acrut wan afella deɣ matcubicu, nta ayamusen isawel wad iknen aslulem, itumas daɣ ḍaret tilli n tawliwin tin dercan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Iceǧrin hulan fel acrut wan afella deɣ matcubicu, nta ayamusen isawel wad iknen aslulem, itumas daɣ ḍaret tilli n tawliwin tin dercan. 
English: The ice is a thin layer of snow, but it is not frozen, and it is not completely frozen.

text: Enceladus amos harat wa ojaran ămlăwlăwan daɣ ǝmǝdlan amos ămlulăw n 90 daɣ temede n annur n tafukt -t ewadan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Enceladus amos harat wa ojaran ămlăwlăwan daɣ ǝmǝdlan amos ămlulăw n 90 daɣ temede n annur n tafukt -t ewadan. 
English: Enceladus is the largest planet in the solar system. It is the largest planet in the solar system.

text: War nhănbăy har aǧenna ămunnen ǝhussiyen ăfella d idraren ǝgutnin wi aɣlaynin. Awa ntukken daɣ eddunya as teddubid aha-tesled as thid ammas n ǝkaham.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War nhănbăy har aǧenna ămunnen ǝhussiyen ăfella d idraren ǝgutnin wi aɣlaynin. Awa ntukken daɣ eddunya as teddubid aha-tesled as thid ammas n ǝkaham. 
English: The war was a major military conflict between the Ottoman Empire and the Ottoman Empire's allies.

text: Amăra-daɣ ful japan. Japan kala ymus ăkal n ǝjǝrwăn cund Britania.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amăra-daɣ ful japan. Japan kala ymus ăkal n ǝjǝrwăn cund Britania. 
English: Tamasheq: Amăra-daɣ ful japan. Japan kala ymus ăkal n ǝjǝrwăn cund Britania.

text: Alwaq wa ǝd ewad Tropical Cyclone Gonu isik net ǝjan isim n saku n tilăfasen n tăšdeyt daɣ awal wan Maldive tan, ewad iddikod n tamădălt n 240 n kilometir daɣ alwaq (149 n kilometir daɣ alwaq).
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa ǝd ewad Tropical Cyclone Gonu isik net ǝjan isim n saku n tilăfasen n tăšdeyt daɣ awal wan Maldive tan, ewad iddikod n tamădălt n 240 n kilometir daɣ alwaq (149 n kilometir daɣ alwaq). 
English: Tropical Cyclone Gonu is a tropical cyclone in the Indian Ocean.

text: Akal wan Turkey, ils iǧelmămen, ila 783,562 n kilometir (300,948 sq mi), desen 755,688 n kilometir tan (291,773 sq mi) llan deɣ tamasna n ataram dagh Asia and 23,764 kilometir tin (9,174 sq mi) deɣ Eroba.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Akal wan Turkey, ils iǧelmămen, ila 783,562 n kilometir (300,948 sq mi), desen 755,688 n kilometir tan (291,773 sq mi) llan deɣ tamasna n ataram dagh Asia and 23,764 kilometir tin (9,174 sq mi) deɣ Eroba. 
English: Turkey is a country in the Middle East, bordered by Iran, Iraq, Syria, and the Mediterranean Sea.

text: Ejjrawen akkal Wan South Shetland dagh awatay wan 1819, ikkalen ejjoutnin tammaghen atawin tllat Bases ajjoutnint, hakked mraw d ssa active dagh awatay wan 2020.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ejjrawen akkal Wan South Shetland dagh awatay wan 1819, ikkalen ejjoutnin tammaghen atawin tllat Bases ajjoutnint, hakked mraw d ssa active dagh awatay wan 2020. 
English: Tamasheq: The South Shetland Islands are a part of the British Isles, and are located in the western part of the archipelago.

text: Apia, tamus tebutut n Samoa, taɣremt tusad deɣ tegzirt tan Upolu, iweḍ daɣ miḍan n muzaɣen nit daw deruɣ 40.000 n adinet.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Apia, tamus tebutut n Samoa, taɣremt tusad deɣ tegzirt tan Upolu, iweḍ daɣ miḍan n muzaɣen nit daw deruɣ 40.000 n adinet. 
English: Apia, Samoa, and Upolu are the only three islands in the archipelago that are inhabited by humans.

text: Alwaq wa ǝd tajuj tămădalt akal , assohăt amǝyiz n asar net fal Amerik d Karayib.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa ǝd tajuj tămădalt akal, assohăt amǝyiz n asar net fal Amerik d Karayib. 
English: The first American to reach the island was Captain John T. Perry, who sailed from New York in 1779.

text: Iga isaddiden daw Maria, ihuharen daɣ ikallen eṭkalnin.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Iga isaddiden daw Maria, ihuharen daɣ ikallen eṭkalnin. 
English: The mother of Mary, Mary Magdalene, was a prostitute.

text: Tiremhitin waǧiɣ ɣas iǧelmamen win mangrove, telat daaɣ haret deɣ midden wi-d-iqqimnin daɣ tiramhatin ti-ṣuhatnin tis-kallad warent tatakurt tan Gangetic.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tiremhitin waǧiɣ ɣas iǧelmamen win mangrove, telat daaɣ haret deɣ midden wi-d-iqqimnin daɣ tiramhatin ti-ṣuhatnin tis-kallad warent tatakurt tan Gangetic. 
English: The mangrove forests are the main habitat of the river, and the river is home to a variety of fish and wildlife.

text: War kăla tessăkin kărti tan ămussu n ăkăl n s ǝtăwăn Geological Survey International Earthquake ,ămussu daɣ ămăḍăl n Island daɣ ǝssǝboɣ hǝn okăyăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War kăla tessăkin kărti tan ămussu n ăkăl n s ǝtăwăn Geological Survey International Earthquake,ămussu daɣ ămăḍăl n Island daɣ ǝssǝboɣ hǝn okăyăn. 
English: The earthquake was felt in the island of Tuvalu.

text: Issunfa daɣ tăkerkurt n idraren win ăfella n Mekka, ǝkahhăm ǝlla daɣ aǧilăl ful eddunet ɣăred.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Issunfa daɣ tăkerkurt n idraren win ăfella n Mekka, ǝkahhăm ǝlla daɣ aǧilăl ful eddunet ɣăred. 
English: The Mekka River is a tributary of the Red River.
